    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been curated to maintain its original showroom integrity, exhibiting flawless exterior surfaces and an interior environment that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously serviced and preserved with exacting standards, it represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. For the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising excellence and a pristine provenance, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark in the pre-owned market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It's in absolute pristine condition\u2014basically looks and smells brand new! I've taken such good care of it, always kept it garaged and serviced. It drives like a dream and is truly a collector's dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is your ride. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive 996.2 wide-body example in showroom condition. This C4S is powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, delivering seamless power through a G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is absolute, featuring a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The viscous multi-plate all-wheel-drive system and Turbo-spec suspension geometry provide unparalleled turn-in precision and lateral stability. Braking is handled by factory-spec four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors, showing no signs of thermal stress. This is a turn-key, preservation-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Full service history. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle presents in true showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and pampered since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint pop as if it just rolled off the assembly line\u2014not a single stone chip or parking lot ding to be found. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any wear, the dashboard is crisp, and it still retains that unmistakable new-car scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a full portfolio of service records from the original dealership confirming every fluid change and inspection was performed on schedule. Every button, dial, and feature functions flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like it has never seen a day of rain. If you demand perfection, your search ends here.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector, exhibiting impeccable cosmetic integrity and mechanical precision. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, it remains in showroom condition, offering a peerless driving experience. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
