      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly pristine, showroom condition\u2014I've babied it since day one! It looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
