    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example remains in concours-level condition, boasting a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry is factory-perfect, utilizing original bushings and dampers for that signature M-chassis feedback. Every mechanical component operates within original tolerances, presenting a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a turn-key analog masterpiece.",
